data.description: This home is situated in a mountain like setting yet located close to town, shopping, hospitals, doctors' offices and schools. This 1380 square foot home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and features wood floors, fireplace, screened in porches on the front and back. Fenced in back yard with a fantastic deck. Great for entertaining, cook outs, rocking chairs and just watching nature. This home is a must see! Call today. FHA with 203K loan acceptable financing.
